item.title: Prayer bpn13024 in Melpa
item.description: *Ya eia, Baha’i nga ik tengpi atenga wingti e wamp pora tek rakdok molk wei. Wamp on e angtinangti molk ken wamp tenta ti ent wanka, wamp we pora angelek molk kumtei. Wamp kolom e amp dam, ya ik mong kägl “nemnga kentmant wä enga kangem” e kelken “nemnga kentmant amp enga bäglam kentamant ampe” i nei. Nanga Anatu, Ya eia, nemnga kentmant wä e, nimnga kentmant wä enga kangem e, nim mondep pelepa, nimnga ugl bä kantepa kon etepa, nin tepa olong ngopa, mel we bä pora tepa bugl ngorom.
